Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.32,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.10,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Destroy the darkness in me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:22.54,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Need to hear a song resounding
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.17,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}In Saecula Saeculorum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:36.57,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}My lost soul and drifting mind
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:44.73,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Oh, give me a reason
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:51.31,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}To keep myself alive
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:58.80,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Without your word, I can't go on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:06.12,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}So send me an answer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:12.34,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}That sweeps across the air
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:20.67,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}To lift me up from all my despair
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:13.38,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Do you remember what you said about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.56,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}"I love your cheekbones"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:29.90,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}One day they will decay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:38.41,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}How do you want them to be shattered?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.46,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Look carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:47.59,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}You're still here alone
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:53.15,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Waiting for midnight blue
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:19:01.77,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Our minds will always race ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:07.06,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Our hearts remain behind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.62,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Can you hear the silent voices?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.93,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Every living thing screams
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.98,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}"Don't leave me here alone!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:33.14,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Your fleeting life will end in this beautiful world
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:37.09,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}All I see is bright
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.04,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}But just for a moment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.66,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}So stay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.21,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Stay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.96,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Stay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:58.10,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Stay
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:02.04,INEG,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Stay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:11.32,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}衝破
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:15.10,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}衝破自己心中的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:22.54,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}想聽響徹四方的歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.17,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:36.57,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}有著迷途的靈魂與漂泊的心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:44.73,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}請告訴我理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:51.31,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}一直這樣活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:58.80,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}沒有理由 我將會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:06.12,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}請給我一個答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:12.34,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}一個穿過疾風的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.10,0:10:20.67,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}請將我從絕望中拯救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:13.38,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}還記得你對我的評價嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.54,0:18:18.56,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}「我喜歡你的顴骨」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:29.90,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}终有一日它將與我化為塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:38.41,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}你希望它如何消逝？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.46,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}目光凝視
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:47.59,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}你在世界上獨身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.47,0:18:53.15,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}夜深人靜 憂鬱便會襲上心頭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:19:01.77,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}我們的想法總是走在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:07.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}心卻被落在了後面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:16.62,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}還聽得見靜靜的聲音嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.93,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}所有的生物在呼喚著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.44,0:19:24.98,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}「請不要把我單獨拋開」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:33.14,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}你虛幻的人生 將在美麗的世界走向終焉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:37.09,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}映入我雙眼的光明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.76,0:19:42.04,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}總是一瞬間的美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.66,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}所以請待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.21,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.96,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:58.10,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}待在這裡
